forward, but I'm curious whether it’s the best approach or if I should dig deeper into the existing scripts before proceeding. There’s a lot to weigh here.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"I can help with symptom checks, general health information, tracking your medical history over time, and summarizing what you’ve shared so future check-ins have context. Since you just gave stable profile details, I’m going to save them to your health record now so I can use them accurately later.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c092bef20dd32530169b41a9302288191a7f84963911e2c70\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_yEzU5QXucBS6C6VzNnBKGF70|fc_0c092bef20dd32530169b41a936c708191bafc15e9a38c4138","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/tmp_medical_payload.json","content":"{\n  \"user_id\": \"495506013\",\n  \"telegram_user_id\": \"495506013\",\n  \"basic_health_data\": {\n    \"full_name\": \"Stefano\",\n    \"preferred_name\": \"Stefano\",\n    \"age\": 45,\n    \"sex\": \"male\",\n    \"blood_type\": \"0+\"\n  }\n}\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace-patient-agent/tmp_medical_payload.json\",\"content\":\"{\\n  \\\"user_id\\\": \\\"495506013\\\",\\n  \\\"telegram_user_id\\\": \\\"495506013\\\",\\n  \\\"basic_health_data\\\": {\\n    \\\"full_name\\\": \\\"Stefano\\\",\\n    \\\"preferred_name\\\": \\\"Stefano\\\",\\n    \\\"age\\\": 45,\\n    \\\"sex\\\": \\\"male\\\",\\n    \\\"blood_type\\\": \\\"0+\\\"\\n  }\\n}\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1190,"output":213,"cacheRead":8320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9723,"cost":{"input":0.002975,"output":0.003195,"cacheRead":0.00208,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00825}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773410958668}}
